stylometry: Some advantages to simulation models are that they let you to immitate real life sittuations while tieing in the unceartainty you might have about a certain problem. It also shows a entire distribution of results with different  values and not just a single result with one value. This can be an advantage because it will let you choose the best possible sollution by laying them all out and showing exactly what each outcome will be. You would use simulation in a management or business situation because you want to minimize your cost and maximize your profit. By running a simulation model it can show you before hand what your outcomes will be allowing you to choose the best one before you actually go through with your idea and run it in your company.
